Tampan-tampanku semuanya menggemaskan dan keren! Aku harap konten NCT berkumpul bersama akan terus ada, dan semoga NCT bisa berkumpul lagi 23 anggota atau dengan NCT anggota baru. Apapun itu semoga kalian semua tetap menjadi bagian NCT. Saat ini winwin sudah mulai bisa aktif lagi bersama wayv dan kedepannya dengan NCT anggota lain, dan aku berharap semoga Lucas ada kabar dan kepastian perihal kedepannya... apakah dia akan kembali dan masih menjadi bagian SM, NCT, WayV, SuperM atau dia ternyata sudah memutuskan kontrak dengan SM, yang pasti kita butuh info lebih lanjut terkait Lucas dan memang kita berharap semoga Lucas tetap stay bersama NCT/WayV dan dibawah naungan SM, serta LabelV.

author: @saraheal1981
text:
SMTreatRenjunBetter *I expect SM to focus more on Renjun and care about Renjun's feelings more than this* cause of the amount of activities, content, promotion of Renjun, the unique opportunity to start doing new things in entertainment industry and participation in nct albums. If you compare it, *RENJUN STILL GETS IT MUCH LESS THAN THE OTHER MEMBERS IN NCT.* And many times it shows that you don't care about Renjun's feelings at all and giving priority to him as the last priority such as 
— *He debuted 6 years but only 9 videos* the company 'intended to make for Renjun' and he's the owner of that content
— *Renjun is the only member in nct dream that has never had content he owns and has 'multiple ep'* or is a moderator of that content (like chenji, JSMR, As chenle wishes, justdoit, 37.5MHz, sun&moon and show!euMarkJungsim) even though he has many activities in his daily life and has always been praised for his variety sense
— The nct show *Renjun only participated in 7 of 29 content and was the only vocal line who had never participated in music space* (1 of 6 mb who didn't participate)​
— He debuted 6 years but there was *only 2 variety shows* in which he was 'representatives' of nct or dream unit and was chosen to participate (20190416 JTBC Idol Room and 2022 The Return of Superman all 3 eps for 41 mins) 
— *He only gets 1 sec vcr* in kcon@LA while the members are mc and has a special vcr longer than 3 mins
— *No ost., no NCT LAB, no feat. or collab with other artists, no series or drama, no mc. Renjun's solo activities that appears on smtown website has only one is to be a RenD at akdong seoul* 
— *Renjun is the only dream member who didn't get any special stage or special performance at sbs gayo* (MK-All i want Christmas, Universe/ JN-Universe, 맛breakdance/ HC-창밖을보라, Universe/ JM-Universe, 맛breakdance/ CL-창밖을보라/ JS-맛breakdance)​ WHY???
— in the smtown concert *He only performed nct dream's songs without any special performances* although he can perform 12월의 인사 song
— in resonance *He isn't the center and has NO SCREEN​ TIME​*
—There is *NO BEHIND THE SCENES of Renjun's photoshoot with ELLE idol Digital magazine and doesn't receive any promotion from sm* even if it sells more than 200.000
— *He was excluded from CF filming* (cosmetic brand) 
— in the title song *Renjun has less and less vocal parts and has the least screen time* (both in MV and performance) despite his position being main vocalist and lead dancer
— *Ending fairy that Renjun only gets 1-2 times per comeback* and fans must always come out and ask for justice. Renjun to get the 2nd ending fairy while other members more than 4 times​
— *Renjun has very few fancams from music shows,* even though his views are ranked 1-4 among all the members. When promoting comeback comes into 2nd week Renjun usually doesn't have a special fancam like facecam, 얼빡직캠 and 입덕직캠 while the other members have both a main fancam and a special fancam 
Other members may only have 1 or 2 problems like this, but Renjun has to face them all. I think this isn't what he deserves as an artist who debuted for 6 years. *Renjun should grow out of his solo activities like the other NCT members have.*
Renjun's fans are always ready to fully support Renjun's work. I think Renjun's fans have devoted quite a lot of money to support him. *SM entertainment should support Renjun fully*
